title: John Lee Hooker - The Complete Chess Folk Blues Sessions (1991)
description:
this CD release includes the complete 'Real Folk Blues' album plus nine previously unreleased songs from the same session


recorded 1966, Chess Studio, Chicago


Lineup:

John Lee Hooker - vocals, electric guitar
probably Eddie Burns - guitar
bass, drums, piano - unknown
